WEBVTT

00:08.509 --> 00:11.512
WHAT ARE YOU AFRAID OF?

00:13.814 --> 00:17.785
DYING IN A PLANE CRASH?

00:17.818 --> 00:22.656
OR CATCHING
AN INCURABLE DISEASE?

00:22.690 --> 00:24.792
GETTING EATEN BY A SHARK.

00:24.825 --> 00:26.660
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:26.694 --> 00:30.498
WHAT YOU SHOULD
REALLY BE AFRAID OF...

00:30.531 --> 00:32.333
IS FAILING THIS CLASS.

00:32.366 --> 00:33.401
[ BOOK SLAMS ]

00:34.102 --> 00:36.003
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:37.971 --> 00:40.274
WHAT, WE SCARE YOU?

00:40.308 --> 00:43.577
FEAR CAN OVERRIDE
RATIONAL THOUGHT.

00:43.611 --> 00:46.847
BEFORE THE NEOCORTEX
CAN EVEN PROCESS A THREAT,

00:46.880 --> 00:49.016
THE AMYGDALA KICKS IN,

00:49.049 --> 00:51.018
AND NOW YOU'RE IN
FIGHT-OR-FLIGHT MODE.

00:51.051 --> 00:56.023
BUT THIS SAME NEUROLOGICAL
PROGRAMMING CAN ALSO SPOOK US.

00:56.056 --> 00:58.092
CAUSE US TO ACT IRRATIONALLY

00:58.126 --> 01:01.695
WHEN, IN REALITY,
THERE'S NOTHING TO WORRY ABOUT.

01:01.729 --> 01:03.797
SO...

01:03.831 --> 01:08.469
CAN WE OVERRIDE
OUR MOST PRIMAL INSTINCTS?

01:08.502 --> 01:14.375
CONDITION OURSELVES
NOT TO REACT OUT OF FEAR?

01:18.412 --> 01:20.114
ALL YOUR MEALS
ARE ON THE FRIDGE.

01:20.148 --> 01:21.682
EVERYTHING
IS COLOR-CODED.

01:21.715 --> 01:24.017
ALL YOU GOT TO DO IS REHEAT THEM
IN THE MICROWAVE.

01:24.051 --> 01:26.520
I DON'T EAT IRRADIATED FOOD.
YOU KNOW THAT.

01:26.554 --> 01:27.521
[ SIGHS ]

01:27.555 --> 01:28.922
OKAY, YOU KNOW, DOC,

01:28.956 --> 01:30.424
MAYBE I COULD JUST DO AN iCHAT
WITH MY FOLKS.

01:30.458 --> 01:32.193
IT'S THEIR 30th ANNIVERSARY,
LEWICKI.

01:32.226 --> 01:33.561
YOU'RE GOING HOME.

01:33.594 --> 01:34.828
I CAN MANAGE ON MY OWN
FOR ONE WEEKEND.

01:34.862 --> 01:37.865
I'LL BE FINE.
WHAT IS AN iCHAT?

01:40.268 --> 01:41.902
I DO SOLEMNLY SWEAR
TO SUPPORT

01:41.935 --> 01:44.071
AND DEFEND THE CONSTITUTION
OF THE UNITED STATES

01:44.104 --> 01:46.407
AGAINST ALL ENEMIES
FOREIGN AND DOMESTIC.

01:46.440 --> 01:49.076
"AND I WILL PROVE
A CRUSHING DISAPPOINTMENT

01:49.109 --> 01:50.544
TO MY CONSTITUENTS."

01:50.578 --> 01:51.779
AND I TAKE THIS
OBLIGATION FREELY.

01:51.812 --> 01:52.913
"I WILL MAKE
SHADY BACKROOM DEALS

01:52.946 --> 01:54.382
"WITH MY FELLOW SENATORS

01:54.415 --> 01:56.284
"AND ACCEPT AS MUCH
SPECIAL-INTEREST MONEY

01:56.317 --> 01:59.353
AS I CAN STUFF
IN MY POCKETS."

01:59.387 --> 02:00.921
YOU VOT FOR RYLAND.

02:00.954 --> 02:02.089
LESSER OF TWO EVILS.

02:02.122 --> 02:03.591
[ HORN HONKS ]

02:03.624 --> 02:05.426
LEWICKI,
YOUR CAB IS HERE!

02:05.459 --> 02:07.261
MAYBE HE'LL SURPRISE YOU.

02:07.295 --> 02:09.863
RYLAND WAS
THE LAST GUY'S PROTéGé.

02:09.897 --> 02:12.366
HE'LL TURN OUT TO BE YET
ANOTHER WALL STREET LACKEY

02:12.400 --> 02:14.268
JUST LIKE EVERYBODY ELSE
IN CONGRESS.

02:14.302 --> 02:16.103
DANIEL,
DON'T BE SO CYNICAL.

02:16.136 --> 02:18.539
EASY FOR YOU TO SAY --
YOU DIDN'T VOTE.

02:18.572 --> 02:19.907
OF COURSE I VOTED.

02:19.940 --> 02:22.075
I WASN'T TALKING TO YOU.

02:22.109 --> 02:26.414
OKAY. UH...
TELL HER I SAY, "HI."

02:26.447 --> 02:28.449
HEY, DOC?

02:28.482 --> 02:30.951
YOU GOT A LETTER.

02:30.984 --> 02:32.453
THERE'S NO STAMP,

02:32.486 --> 02:35.289
SO IT MUST HAVE BEEN
HAND-DELIVERED FROM SOME GUY --

02:35.323 --> 02:37.024
WESLEY SUMTER?

02:38.726 --> 02:41.128
WHO'S WESLEY SUMTER?

02:41.161 --> 02:43.464
HE'S A F[ HORN HONKS ]

02:43.497 --> 02:44.498
WOULD YOU GET OUT
OF HERE ALREADY?

02:44.532 --> 02:46.099
[ Sighing ]
ALL RIGHT.

02:46.133 --> 02:48.402
OKAY, UH,
I WILL SEE YOU ON SUNDAY.

02:48.436 --> 02:49.970
DON'T DO ANYTHING
CRAZY, DOC.

02:50.003 --> 02:51.472
NO PROMISES.

02:51.505 --> 02:53.907
I CAN CANCEL.

02:53.941 --> 02:57.144
IT'S A JOKE.
I'M JOKING. GO!

02:57.177 --> 02:58.512
[ SIGHS ]

03:03.384 --> 03:05.052
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

03:08.489 --> 03:10.824
DANIEL, WHAT'S WRONG?

03:38.218 --> 03:40.354
[ GASPS ]
OH [BLEEP] IT!

03:40.388 --> 03:43.691
Wesley, are you trying
to give me a coronary?!

03:43.724 --> 03:45.058
I'm sorry.
I-i didn't mean to scare you.

03:45.092 --> 03:46.827
Well, what's with
the melodrama, huh?

03:46.860 --> 03:48.329
T-T-The note, the meeting
at 2:00 in the morning?

03:48.362 --> 03:50.130
What the [bleep]
is going on?!

03:50.163 --> 03:52.266
I'll explain everything,
okay, b-but not here.

03:55.736 --> 03:57.237
People could be listening.

03:58.506 --> 04:01.309
Come on. Come on.

04:06.814 --> 04:10.718
Okay, this is good.
This is good, this is good.

04:10.751 --> 04:15.389
LISTEN, THIS NEW SENATOR,
RYLAND...

04:15.423 --> 04:17.991
YOU REMEMBER WHAT HAPPENED
TO HIS PREDECESSOR?

04:18.025 --> 04:22.229
WELL, YEAH, HIS PRIVATE JET FLEW
INTO THE SIDE OF A MOUNTAIN.

04:22.262 --> 04:23.897
HIS PLANE WAS SABOTAGED.

04:23.931 --> 04:26.567
SABOTAGED? BY WHOM?

04:26.600 --> 04:30.738
LARRY CRAWFORD, C.E.O.
OF THE VERTERON CORPORATION.

04:30.771 --> 04:33.240
THE ELECTRONICS COMPANY?

04:33.273 --> 04:36.076
YEAH. PAULSON...

04:36.109 --> 04:38.912
PAULSON CHAIRED -- HE CHAIRED
A-A COMMITTEE THAT --

04:38.946 --> 04:40.914
THAT -- THAT --
THAT WAS --

04:40.948 --> 04:43.584
WAS GONNA PASS A...
A CLEAN-ENERGY BILL

04:43.617 --> 04:46.186
THAT WOULD HAVE COST
VERTERON BILLIONS.

04:46.219 --> 04:47.688
OKAY.

04:47.721 --> 04:50.891
OKAY, S-SO THEY STOOD TO GAIN
FROM PAULSON'S DEATH,

04:50.924 --> 04:53.060
BUT WHAT MAKES YOU THINK
THEY HAD ANYTHING TO DO
WITH THE PLANE CRASH?

04:53.093 --> 04:55.062
THEY MADE THE -- [ SNIFFS ]
THE ANTI-COLLISION SYSTEM

04:55.095 --> 04:57.097
THAT SHOULD HAVE PREVENTED
THE ACCIDENT.

04:57.130 --> 04:59.600
NOT ONLY THAT, BUT --
BUT -- BUT -- [ GULPS ]

04:59.633 --> 05:03.103
ONE OF THEIR ENGINEERS,
BRIAN WILLINGHAM,

05:03.136 --> 05:05.606
DIED RIGHT AFTER HE FOUND OUT
ABOUT THE SABOTAGE.

05:05.639 --> 05:09.076
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

05:09.109 --> 05:10.578
T-THEY SAID
IT WAS SUICIDE,

05:10.611 --> 05:12.746
BUT -- BUT I THINK
IT WAS MURDER.

05:12.780 --> 05:15.248
WESLEY, W-W-WHAT ARE YOU
COMING TO ME WITH THIS FOR?

05:15.282 --> 05:16.784
YOU SHOULD GO
TO THE POLICE.

05:16.817 --> 05:19.453
[ SCOFFS ]
I TRIED.

05:19.487 --> 05:20.954
I TRIED,
BUT -- BUT NO ONE --

05:20.988 --> 05:23.557
NO ONE WOULD
TAKE ME SERIOUSLY.

05:23.591 --> 05:26.259
E-EXCEPT FOR ONE GUY,
THIS -- THIS REPORTER,

05:26.293 --> 05:28.161
UH, UH,
FROM THE STAR-HERALD,

05:28.195 --> 05:31.064
BUT THEN -- BUT THEN
HE, UH -- HE DROVE HIS CAR

05:31.098 --> 05:33.367
OFF OF A ROAD,
AND HE BROKE HIS NECK.

05:33.401 --> 05:35.102
NOW,
THAT'S THREE MEN DEAD,

05:35.135 --> 05:37.971
AND I'M GONNA BE THE FOURTH
IF THIS COMPANY ISN'T STOPPED.

05:38.005 --> 05:40.140
WESLEY,
I UNDERSTAND YOU'RE SCARED,

05:40.173 --> 05:43.243
A-A-AND IF WHAT YOU'RE SAYING
IS TRUE, IT'S TERRIBLE.

05:43.276 --> 05:45.245
BUT...

05:45.278 --> 05:48.582
ISN'T IT POSSIBLE YOU'RE MAKING
CONNECTIONS THAT...

05:48.616 --> 05:50.984
THAT AREN'T REALLY THERE?

05:51.018 --> 05:53.153
[ SCOFFING ]

05:53.186 --> 05:55.088
[ GULPS ]
I READ ABOUT YOUR WORK

05:55.122 --> 05:57.290
IN THE SARIN BOMBER CASE,
AND I THOUGHT THAT --

05:57.324 --> 06:00.093
THAT IF ANYONE WERE TO HELP ME
BLOW THE LID OFF THIS THING,

06:00.127 --> 06:02.129
IT WOULD BE YOU,
BUT I GUESS I WAS WRONG.

06:02.162 --> 06:04.632
W-W-WAIT, WESLEY.
L-LOOK, LOOK.

06:04.665 --> 06:07.300
THERE'S AN FBI AGENT
THAT I KNOW.

06:07.334 --> 06:11.004
I-I'LL ASK HER
TO LOOK INTO IT, OKAY?

06:12.372 --> 06:14.007
THANK YOU.

06:14.041 --> 06:16.043
THANK YOU, PROFESSOR.

06:18.011 --> 06:21.181
WAIT, OH.
EVERYTHING --

06:21.214 --> 06:22.683
EVERYTHING THAT --

06:22.716 --> 06:24.618
THAT YOU NEED TO KNOW IS --
IS IN HERE.

06:24.652 --> 06:27.921
HERE IT IS.
HERE IT IS.

06:27.955 --> 06:29.823
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

06:29.857 --> 06:32.993
[ LAUGHS ]
I-I KNEW YOU WOULD HELP.

06:33.026 --> 06:35.262
I --

06:40.167 --> 06:41.469
WESLEY.

06:52.913 --> 06:55.382
HEADING OUT?
IT'S NOT EVEN 3:00 A.M. YET.

06:55.415 --> 06:58.018
YEAH, THOUGHT I'D KNOCK OFF
A LITTLE EARLY.

06:58.051 --> 06:59.687
[ CHUCKLES ]

06:59.720 --> 07:02.255
STICK AROUND.
I'LL BUY YOU BREAKFAST.

07:02.289 --> 07:03.691
THERE WILL BE BACON.

07:03.724 --> 07:05.358
YOU DO KNOW
MY WEAKNESS.

07:05.392 --> 07:07.528
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

07:07.561 --> 07:10.030
MORETTI.

07:10.063 --> 07:13.567
D-DANIEL, SLOW DOWN.

07:13.601 --> 07:15.368
UH, OKAY, JUST STAY CALM.
I'LL BE RIGHT OVER.

07:15.402 --> 07:17.404
CALL CPD.

07:17.437 --> 07:19.372
THERE'S BEEN A MURDER
AT THE CLMU CAMPUS --

07:19.406 --> 07:20.407
COURTYARD BY THE CHAPEL.

07:24.277 --> 07:28.048
[ POLICE ROGER.CHATTER ]

07:28.081 --> 07:29.750
WE HAVE A SLIGHT PROBLEM.

07:29.783 --> 07:33.253
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.
WHERE'S WESLEY?

07:33.286 --> 07:34.588
I DON'T KNOW.
YOU TELL ME.

07:34.622 --> 07:36.089
I WAS THE FIRST PERSON
ON THE SCENE,

07:36.123 --> 07:39.459
AND THERE WAS NO BODY
WHEN I GOT HERE.

07:46.233 --> 07:47.901
[ CLASSICAL MUSIC PLAYING ]

08:02.750 --> 08:03.884
DANIEL?

08:03.917 --> 08:05.152
[ MUSIC STOPS ]

08:05.185 --> 08:06.920
LISTEN, CPD's BEEN
INTERVIEWING FACULTY

08:06.954 --> 08:08.421
AND STUDENTS FOR HOURS.

08:08.455 --> 08:10.390
NO ONE SAW ANY SHOOTING
OR ANYONE FLEEING THE SCENE.

08:10.423 --> 08:11.925
THIS AREA O-OF THE CAMPUS
IS DESERTED AT NIGHT.

08:11.959 --> 08:13.594
YOU KNOW THAT.

08:13.627 --> 08:16.429
CRIME TECHS DIDN'T TURN UP
ANY BLOOD RESIDUE, EITHER.

08:16.463 --> 08:19.299
WELL, OBVIOUSLY SOMEBODY'S
CLEANED UP THE CRIME SCENE.

08:19.332 --> 08:21.134
THESE...

08:21.168 --> 08:24.605
THESE ARE JUST NEWSPAPER
CLIPPINGS, OKAY?

08:24.638 --> 08:26.273
THERE'S NO EVIDENCE HERE.

08:28.642 --> 08:30.644
I GOT TO BE HONEST WITH YOU --
THE BOSS IS [BLEEP]

08:30.678 --> 08:32.312
FORENSICS HAS BEEN OUT HERE
ALL NIGHT.

08:32.345 --> 08:33.781
I GOT TO SEND
THESE PEOPLE HOME.

08:33.814 --> 08:35.448
WELL, I'M SORRY
IF WESLEY'S MURDER

08:35.482 --> 08:37.350
HAS INCONVENIENCED
THE CRIME LAB.

08:37.384 --> 08:39.953
DANIEL, LISTEN.

08:39.987 --> 08:43.123
REARDON KNOWS ABOUT YOUR...
CONDITION.

08:43.156 --> 08:46.326
SHE DOESN'T CONSIDER YOU A...
RELIABLE WITNESS.

08:46.359 --> 08:48.662
[ SCOFFS ]

08:48.696 --> 08:51.164
WE RAN THE NAME
YOU GAVE US.

08:51.198 --> 08:52.700
THERE'S NO RECORD
OF A WESLEY SUMTER

08:52.733 --> 08:55.468
ANYWHERE IN CHICAGO
OR HAVING EVER ATTENDED CLMU.

08:55.502 --> 08:57.137
I TOLD YOU,
HE ONLY AUDITED MY CLASS.

08:57.170 --> 08:58.839
I-I-I DON'T KNOW
IF HE EVER REGISTERED.

08:58.872 --> 09:01.174
AND HE WOULDN'T BE THE FIRST
PERSON TO KEEP HIS NAME...

09:01.208 --> 09:03.176
out of
a government database.

09:03.210 --> 09:04.845
LISTEN,
YOU KNOW I'VE GOT YOUR BACK,

09:04.878 --> 09:07.014
AND I'M GONNA KEEP DIGGING,
EVEN IF REARDON DOESN'T LIKE IT,

09:07.047 --> 09:10.483
BUT I...
I GOT TO ASK YOU...

09:10.517 --> 09:13.186
IS IT POSSIBLE
THAT YOU SAW SOMETHING

09:13.220 --> 09:14.888
THAT DIDN'T REALLY HAPPEN?

09:26.033 --> 09:27.400
Daniel: LOOK AT THIS.

09:27.434 --> 09:30.037
IT SAYS THE NTSB's REPORT
ON THE PLANE CRASH

09:30.070 --> 09:31.805
HAS BEEN DELAYED A THIRD TIME.

09:31.839 --> 09:33.540
MAYBE WESLEY WAS RIGHT.

09:33.573 --> 09:36.209
M-MAYBE THE SENATOR'S PLANE
REALLY WAS SABOTAGED.

09:36.243 --> 09:37.544
Natalie:
DANIEL, THE STORY HE TOLD

09:37.577 --> 09:39.512
IS EXACTLY THE KIND
OF PARANOID SCENARIO

09:39.546 --> 09:41.414
THAT A SCHIZOPHRENIC
WOULD COME UP WITH.

09:41.448 --> 09:43.083
YOU THINK WESLEY
WAS MENTALLY ILL?

09:43.116 --> 09:45.518
I DON'T KNOW.
BUT YOU ARE.

09:45.552 --> 09:47.054
MAYBE KATE'S RIGHT.

09:47.087 --> 09:48.922
YOU'RE THE ONLY ONE
WHO SAW THIS GUY.

09:48.956 --> 09:52.259
WELL, I-IF WESLEY WASN'T REAL,
WHERE DID ALL THESE COME FROM?

09:52.292 --> 09:54.695
YOU HAVE A CLOSET FULL
OF OLD NEWSPAPERS.

09:54.728 --> 09:57.064
LEWICKI JUST -- JUST SAVES THOSE
FOR THE CROSSWORDS.

09:57.097 --> 09:58.431
AND WHAT ABOUT
THE LETTER?

09:58.465 --> 09:59.767
YOU DO HAVE A TYPEWRITER.

09:59.800 --> 10:02.269
YOU'RE SAYING
I SENT IT TO MYSELF.

10:02.302 --> 10:03.837
HAVE YOU BEEN TAKING
YOUR MEDS?

10:03.871 --> 10:06.573
LEWICKI PICKED UP A PRESCRIPTION
FOR ME WEEKS AGO.

10:06.606 --> 10:08.208
YOU KNOW THAT.

10:08.241 --> 10:09.777
I DIDN'T ASK YOU IF YOU HAD
A PRESCRIPTION FILLED.

10:09.810 --> 10:11.645
I ASKED IF YOU WERE TAKING
YOUR MEDS.

10:11.679 --> 10:14.247
IF WE OPEN THE MEDICINE CABINET
AND COUNTED THE PILLS,

10:14.281 --> 10:17.250
HOW MANY WOULD BE LEFT?

10:17.284 --> 10:18.919
YOU'VE BEEN UNDER
A LOT OF STRESS

10:18.952 --> 10:20.587
SINCE YOU STARTED WORKING
WITH KATE AGAIN,

10:20.620 --> 10:22.756
BUT I DON'T THINK YOUR
COPING MECHANISMS ARE ENOUGH

10:22.790 --> 10:24.925
TO KEEP YOU
ON AN EVEN KEEL ANYMORE.

10:24.958 --> 10:26.760
IF YOU WON'T TAKE THE MEDICATION
FOR YOURSELF,

10:26.794 --> 10:29.096
THEN DO IT FOR HER.

10:29.129 --> 10:30.798
W-WHAT'S THAT
SUPPOSED TO MEAN?

10:30.831 --> 10:32.966
KATE'S OUT THERE TRYING TO FIND
EVIDENCE FOR A MURDER

10:33.000 --> 10:34.902
THAT MIGHT HAVE ONLY HAPPENED
IN YOUR MIND.

10:34.935 --> 10:38.538
THINK ABOUT HER CAREER,
HER REPUTATION.

10:38.571 --> 10:40.473
WHAT IF YOU'RE WRONG?

10:40.507 --> 10:41.842
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

10:46.680 --> 10:49.449
NEVER UNDERESTIMATE THE POWER
OF SHOE LEATHER.

10:49.482 --> 10:51.719
MIGHT WANT TO MAKE US
SOME POPCORN.

10:57.925 --> 10:59.426
WHERE DID YOU GET THIS?

10:59.459 --> 11:02.395
A STUDENT CAUGHT THE WHOLE THING
ON HIS CELLPHONE.

11:02.429 --> 11:05.198
[ SIGHS ]
IT REALLY HAPPENED.

11:07.968 --> 11:09.937
I'M SORRY I DOUBTED YOU.

11:09.970 --> 11:14.241
I UNDERSTAND WHY YOU DID.

11:15.843 --> 11:18.145
LOOK, I'VE ASKED THE CART UNIT
TO ENHANCE THE TAPE,

11:18.178 --> 11:20.981
TRY TO I.D. THE SNIPER.

11:21.014 --> 11:23.851
SO WESLEY REALLY WAS
ONTO SOMETHING BIG,

11:23.884 --> 11:26.353
A-A-AND WHOEVER KILLED
THE SENATOR

11:26.386 --> 11:28.455
WAS TRYING
TO SILENCE HIM.

11:28.488 --> 11:30.190
JUST SO WE'RE CLEAR,

11:30.223 --> 11:32.525
I'M NOT INVESTIGATING SOME
JAMES BOND MURDER PLOT, OKAY?

11:32.559 --> 11:34.461
I'M JUST LOOKING FOR A GUY
WITH A CROSSBOW.

11:34.494 --> 11:37.330
DO WE HAVE AN ADDRESS YET
FOR WESLEY OR NEXT OF KIN?

11:37.364 --> 11:39.699
NO, AND THERE'S NO PHYSICAL
EVIDENCE AT THE CRIME SCENE.

11:39.733 --> 11:41.969
WELL, IF WE CAN'T FIND HIS BODY,
THEN MAYBE --

11:42.002 --> 11:44.137
MAYBE LOOKING INTO
WHAT HE WAS INVESTIGATING

11:44.171 --> 11:45.605
WILL LEAD US TO THE KILLER.

11:45.638 --> 11:47.340
YOU SAID WESLEY WAS TALKING
TO A REPORTER?

11:47.374 --> 11:48.375
[ SNAPS FINGERS ]
YES.

11:48.408 --> 11:50.878
YES!
FROM THE, UH...

11:50.911 --> 11:52.545
STAR-HERALD.

11:52.579 --> 11:56.049
UH...UH...

11:56.083 --> 11:57.717
HERE.

11:57.751 --> 11:59.486
DAVID ALCOTT.

12:02.355 --> 12:04.324
BUT HE'S DEAD.

12:04.357 --> 12:07.527
MAYBE HIS BOSS AT THE PAPER
HAS SOME INFORMATION ON WESLEY.

12:07.560 --> 12:09.863
OH, YOU MUST MEAN
"CRAZY" WESLEY.

12:09.897 --> 12:12.532
OH, HE CALLS THE ASSIGNMENT DESK
AT ALL HOURS

12:12.565 --> 12:15.702
AND LEAVES THESE BIZARRE
MESSAGES ON OUR VOICEMAIL.

12:15.735 --> 12:17.871
ONCE, HE CALLED FROM A WAREHOUSE
IN NEW MEXICO,

12:17.905 --> 12:20.040
CLAIMED HE HAD FOUND
THE SOUND STAGE

12:20.073 --> 12:21.208
WHERE NASA HAD FAKED
THE LUNAR LANDING.

12:21.241 --> 12:24.211
THE GUY IS ABSOLUTELY NUTS.

12:24.244 --> 12:27.014
SOME MYTHS, IT SEEMS,
NEVER DIE.

12:27.047 --> 12:31.184
BUT PUTTING A MAN ON THE MOON
WAS MY GREATEST ACCOMPLISHMENT.

12:31.218 --> 12:33.020
50 YEARS LATER,

12:33.053 --> 12:34.754
AND THEY'RE STILL TRYING
TO UNDERMINE MY PRESIDENCY.

12:34.788 --> 12:36.589
DO YOU HAVE ANY CONTACT INFO
FOR WESLEY --

12:36.623 --> 12:38.258
A PHONE NUMBER, MAYBE?

12:38.291 --> 12:39.692
I'LL LOOK,
BUT I DOUBT IT.

12:39.726 --> 12:42.529
YOU KNOW,
THE GUY IS A TOTAL WHACK JOB.

12:42.562 --> 12:44.731
WHY ARE YOU ASKING
ABOUT HIM, ANYWAY?

12:44.764 --> 12:47.700
WELL, HE WAS MURDERED
LAST NIGHT.

12:47.734 --> 12:50.703
YES. YES.

12:50.737 --> 12:52.105
UH, BUT BEFORE HE DIED,

12:52.139 --> 12:53.573
HE TOLD ME HE TIPPED OFF
ONE OF YOUR REPORTERS,

12:53.606 --> 12:56.543
WHO ALSO DIED RECENTLY.

12:56.576 --> 12:57.878
YOU MEAN DAVID ALCOTT?

12:57.911 --> 13:00.447
DO YOU KNOW WHAT ALCOTT
WAS WORKING ON?

13:00.480 --> 13:02.115
NO, DAVID KEPT HIS CARDS
PRETTY CLOSE TO HIS VEST.

13:02.149 --> 13:04.084
HE WAS ALWAYS AFRAID
OF BEING SCOOPED.

13:04.117 --> 13:05.585
WHAT ABOUT HIS COMPUTER?

13:05.618 --> 13:08.088
HE NEVER USED ONE.
HE WAS PRETTY OLD-SCHOOL.

13:08.121 --> 13:10.123
BUT WE CLEANED OUT
HIS DESK

13:10.157 --> 13:12.625
AND THREW EVERYTHING
IN A BOX.

13:12.659 --> 13:16.897
I COULD GET MY ASSISTANT
TO FIND THE BOX FOR YOU.

13:16.930 --> 13:19.732
WESLEY'S NAME IS MENTIONED,

13:19.766 --> 13:21.734
BUT THERE'S NOTHING
IN THE REPORTER'S NOTES

13:21.768 --> 13:23.170
THAT AREN'T ALSO
IN THE NEWSPAPER CLIPPINGS.

13:27.507 --> 13:29.309
PLEIADES.

13:29.342 --> 13:31.879
SEVEN SISTERS --
GREEK MYTHOLOGY.

13:33.947 --> 13:36.149
WHAT, YOU THINK THE ONLY CLASS
I TOOK IN COLLEGE WAS YOURS?

13:36.183 --> 13:37.985
YOU THINK IT MEANS
SOMETHING?

13:38.018 --> 13:40.320
GOT TO ADMIT, THOUGHT
IT WAS A WILD-GOOSE CHASE.

13:40.353 --> 13:42.155
I MEAN, WHAT THE [BLEEP]
DOES A CAMPUS SHOOTING

13:42.189 --> 13:44.157
HAVE TO DO WITH THE DEATH
OF A UNITED STATES SENATOR?

13:44.191 --> 13:47.594
BUT I THINK I ACTUALLY FOUND
A CONNECTION.

13:47.627 --> 13:49.662
WELL,
WILL MIRACLES NEVER CEASE?

13:49.696 --> 13:52.099
I RAN ALCOTT'S
CELLPHONE RECORDS.

13:52.132 --> 13:53.633
THERE WERE SEVEN CALLS

13:53.666 --> 13:57.004
BETWEEN HIM AND A CELL
REGISTERED TO HELEN PAULSON.

13:57.037 --> 13:58.338
W-WIFE OF
THE LATE SENATOR?

13:58.371 --> 14:00.340
WHY WOULD SHE BE CALLING
A REPORTER?

14:00.373 --> 14:01.942
HELEN PAULSON.

14:01.975 --> 14:03.476
IF THE SENATOR WAS MURDERED,
HE MAY HAVE BEEN THREATENED.

14:03.510 --> 14:04.811
AND MAYBE HIS WIFE
CAN GIVE US A NAME.

14:06.379 --> 14:10.017
"INSIDERS SAY THE GOVERNOR
HAS DECIDED

14:10.050 --> 14:13.020
TO APPOINT HELEN PAULSON TO FILL
HER HUSBAND'S SENATE SEAT."

14:13.053 --> 14:15.355
BUT THE GOVERNMENT
DIDN'T APPOINT HER.

14:15.388 --> 14:17.690
MAYBE THE INSIDERS
WERENO.ONG.

14:17.724 --> 14:20.994
"IN A HASTILY CALLED
PRESS CONFERENCE,

14:21.028 --> 14:22.662
"MRS. PAULSON ANNOUNCED
SHE WAS DECLINING

14:22.695 --> 14:24.097
"THE GOVERNOR'S OFFER

14:24.131 --> 14:25.398
"AND INSTEAD URGED HIM
TO CALL A SPECIAL ELECTION

14:25.432 --> 14:27.200
"TO LET THE PEOPLE
OF ILLINOIS DECIDE

14:27.234 --> 14:30.170
WHO THEIR NEXT SENATOR
WILL BE."

14:30.203 --> 14:31.871
SHE ENDORSED
SCOTT RYLAND.

14:31.905 --> 14:33.974
WHY WOULD ANYBODY TURN DOWN
A SENATE SEAT?

14:34.007 --> 14:35.508
I'VE GOT AN IDEA.

14:35.542 --> 14:37.310
HOW ABOUT INSTEAD OF
STANDING HERE SPECULATING,

14:37.344 --> 14:38.411
WE JUST ASK HER?

14:42.449 --> 14:45.318
OKAY, GOT IT, GOT IT.

14:47.087 --> 14:49.022
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

14:49.056 --> 14:52.025
AGENT MORETTI, FBI.
IS THAT HELEN PAULSON?

14:52.059 --> 14:54.561
YEAH.
SHE'S IN PREWHAT HAPPENED?

14:54.594 --> 14:56.329
DON'T KNOW. SHE WAS UNRESPONSIVE
WHEN WE GOT HERE.

14:56.363 --> 14:59.232
THE MAID FOUND HER LIKE THIS
AND JUST CALLED 911.

14:59.266 --> 15:00.700
EXCUSE ME.

15:03.536 --> 15:06.306
THIS IS NO COINCIDENCE,
PROFESSOR.

15:06.339 --> 15:08.708
IT'S DALLAS
ALL OVER AGAIN.

15:10.443 --> 15:13.180
CLEARLY, SOMEONE TRIED TO
ASSASSINATE THE SENATOR'S WIFE.

15:15.782 --> 15:17.617
[ SIREN WAILING ]

15:26.926 --> 15:29.729
MRS. PAULSON IS DISPLAYING SIGNS
OF NEURODEGENERATION

15:29.762 --> 15:31.398
AND CONGESTIVE
HEART FAILURE.

15:31.431 --> 15:32.899
ANY IDEA
WHAT'S CAUSING IT?

15:32.932 --> 15:34.067
WISH I COULD SAY.

15:34.101 --> 15:35.435
HER PRIMARY PHYSICIAN SAID

15:35.468 --> 15:37.737
SHE WAS THE PICTURE OF HEALTH
A MONTH AGO.

15:37.770 --> 15:40.073
I'M JUST PUMPING HER
FULL OF ANTIBIOTICS

15:40.107 --> 15:41.408
UNTIL THE LABS COME BACK.

15:41.441 --> 15:42.709
CAN WE TALK TO HER?

15:42.742 --> 15:43.743
YEAH,
FOR A FEW MINUTES.

15:49.449 --> 15:54.087
MRS. PAULSON. HI.
THIS IS DR. PIERCE.

15:54.121 --> 15:56.423
I'M AGENT MORETTI,
WITH THE FBI.

15:56.456 --> 15:59.259
YES.

15:59.292 --> 16:01.428
LISTEN, YOU SPOKE RECENTLY
WITH A NEWSPAPER REPORTER,

16:01.461 --> 16:02.996
DAVID ALCOTT.

16:03.030 --> 16:05.165
CAN YOU TELL ME WHAT THE TWO
OF YOU TALKED ABOUT?

16:06.966 --> 16:09.936
HE SAID...

16:09.969 --> 16:14.274
THAT SOMEONE CAUSED
TED'S PLANE TO CRASH.

16:14.307 --> 16:16.309
HE SAID HE HAD EVIDENCE.

16:18.145 --> 16:20.580
DID -- DID HE TELL YOU
WHO HE THOUGHT DID IT?

16:20.613 --> 16:22.415
LAWRENCE CRAWFORD.

16:22.449 --> 16:25.418
C.E.O. OF VERTERON.
WESLEY WAS RIGHT.

16:25.452 --> 16:28.455
DID THE REPORTER SAY WHAT KIND
OF EVIDENCE HE HAD?

16:28.488 --> 16:31.791
NO, BUT...

16:31.824 --> 16:33.293
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

16:33.326 --> 16:36.129
...I-I TOLD HIM
HE MUST BE MISTAKEN.

16:36.163 --> 16:38.298
[ WHIMPERS ]

16:38.331 --> 16:40.633
LARRY WOULD NEVER
HURT TED.

16:40.667 --> 16:43.970
HE'S ONE OF
OUR CLOSEST FRIENDS.

16:44.003 --> 16:45.438
MRS. PAULSON...

16:45.472 --> 16:48.308
WHY DID YOU TURN DOWN
YOUR HUSBAND'S SENATE SEAT?

16:49.842 --> 16:51.978
SENATE?

16:52.011 --> 16:53.046
YES.

16:54.514 --> 16:56.816
IS TED HERE?

16:56.849 --> 16:58.318
[ MONITOR BEEPING RAPIDLY ]

16:58.351 --> 17:00.487
CLEAR THE ROOM!

17:00.520 --> 17:01.721
[ FLATLINE ]

17:09.028 --> 17:10.997
THANK YOU FOR SEEING US
ON A SATURDAY, MR. CRAWFORD.

17:11.030 --> 17:12.865
NO PROBLEM. I HOPE
THIS WON'T TAKE LONG, THOUGH.

17:12.899 --> 17:14.667
MY SON'S SOCCER GAME STARTS
IN ABOUT AN HOUR.

17:14.701 --> 17:16.136
OH, WE'LL GET YOU THERE
ON TIME.

17:16.169 --> 17:17.837
I SEE YOU HAVE AN INTEREST
IN ASTRONOMY.

17:17.870 --> 17:19.072
IT'S A HOBBY.

17:19.106 --> 17:20.840
AND WHAT
ARE THO STARS?

17:20.873 --> 17:23.076
THOSE ARE THE PLEIADES.

17:23.110 --> 17:25.212
THE SEVHMM.ISTERS.

17:26.879 --> 17:28.948
YOU DIDN'T COME HERE
TO TALK ASTRONOMY.

17:28.981 --> 17:31.017
NO.
IT'S ABOUT HELEN PAULSON.

17:31.050 --> 17:32.952
WE SPOKE WITH HER
A FEW HOURS AGO,

17:32.985 --> 17:34.987
JUST BEFORE SHE...DIED.

17:35.021 --> 17:37.490
HELEN DIED?
WHAT HAPPENED?

17:37.524 --> 17:39.659
WE DON'T KNOW,
BUT AN AUTOPSY HAS BEEN ORDERED.

17:39.692 --> 17:41.794
SO MUCH TRAGEDY
FOR ONE FAMILY.

17:41.828 --> 17:43.163
SHE TOLD US THAT SOMEBODY
AT THIS COMPANY

17:43.196 --> 17:44.464
WAS INVOLVED IN
HER HUSBAND'S PLANE CRASH.

17:44.497 --> 17:45.865
YEAH, SHE TOLD ME
THE SAME THING.

17:45.898 --> 17:47.834
A REPORTER WAS MAKING
WILD ALLEGATIONS.

17:47.867 --> 17:49.736
I TOLD HELEN I WAS SURE
IT WASN'T TRUE

17:49.769 --> 17:51.538
BUT I'D LOOK INTO IT,
WHICH I DID.

17:51.571 --> 17:53.540
AND, OF COURSE,
THERE WAS NOTHING TO IT.

17:53.573 --> 17:56.343
BUT VERTERON DID MANUFACTURE
THE TERRAIN-AVOIDANCE SYSTEM

17:56.376 --> 17:58.311
THAT WAS INSTALLED
IN THE SENATOR'S PLANE.

17:58.345 --> 17:59.379
YES, THAT'S TRUE.

17:59.412 --> 18:01.047
SO IF THE SYSTEM
WAS WORKING,

18:01.080 --> 18:02.982
HE SHOULDN'T HAVE FLOWN
INTO THE SIDE

18:03.015 --> 18:05.051
OF A MOUNTAIN
ON A CLEAR NIGHT.

18:05.084 --> 18:07.320
THE T.A.S.
WAS WORKING PERFECTLY.

18:07.354 --> 18:08.588
YOU SOUND PRETTY SURE
OF THAT.

18:08.621 --> 18:10.257
WE EXAMINED DEBRIS
FROM THE PLANE.

18:10.290 --> 18:11.491
YOU EXAMINED?

18:11.524 --> 18:13.059
IS IT STANDARD
PROCEDURE FOR --

18:13.092 --> 18:15.695
FOR A COMPANY TO DETERMINE
ITS OWN CULPABILITY

18:15.728 --> 18:16.996
IN A FATAL PLANE CRASH?

18:17.029 --> 18:19.098
THE NTSB ASKED
FOR OUR COOPERATION.

18:19.132 --> 18:20.567
WE GAVE IT TO THEM.

18:20.600 --> 18:22.735
YOU DON'T BELIEVE ME,
HAVE A LOOK AT THIS.

18:22.769 --> 18:24.404
THE NTSB REPORT.

18:24.437 --> 18:27.407
HOW DO YOU HAVE THIS?
THIS HASN'T BEEN RELEASED YET.

18:27.440 --> 18:28.908
THEY'RE RELEASING IT
MONDAY. THEY E-MAILED
ME AN ADVANCED COPY.

18:28.941 --> 18:30.443
[ Laughing ]
AND THEY SAY THE GOVERNMENT

18:30.477 --> 18:32.078
IS TOO COZY
WITH BIG BUSINESS.

18:32.111 --> 18:34.347
AS YOU CAN SEE, A HYDRAULICS
FAILURE CAUSED THE CRASH.

18:34.381 --> 18:35.915
OUR SYSTEM HAD NOTHING
TO DO WITH IT.

18:35.948 --> 18:38.151
THIS SO-CALLED REPORT
IS MEANINGLESS.

18:38.185 --> 18:40.720
YOUR INVESTIGATORS HAVE HAD
MONTHS TO FALSIFY THIS DATA!

18:40.753 --> 18:42.255
I GOT A GAME TO GET TO.

18:42.289 --> 18:45.057
ANY MORE QUESTIONS,
YOU TALK TO MY LAWYER.

19:01.341 --> 19:03.343
DANIEL,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

19:06.513 --> 19:08.615
CRAWFORD HAD A PAINTING
OF THESE STARS

19:08.648 --> 19:11.117
PROMINENTLY DISPLAYED
IN HIS CONFERENCE ROOM.

19:11.150 --> 19:12.552
IT CAN'T BE A COINCIDENCE

19:12.585 --> 19:14.787
THAT THE REPORTER WROTE DOWN
THE NAME "PLEIADES."

19:14.821 --> 19:18.258
THERE HAS TO BE A PATTERN OR
A SYMBOL THAT MEANS SOMETHING.

19:18.291 --> 19:19.926
WHAT THE [BLEEP]
AM I LOOKING FOR?

19:19.959 --> 19:22.762
MAYBE THE STARS ARE SIGNIFICANT
IN SOME OTHER WAY.

19:22.795 --> 19:25.432
WHAT IS THEIR HISTORY?
WHERE DO THEIR NAMES COME FROM?

19:25.465 --> 19:26.966
GREEK MYTHOLOGY.

19:26.999 --> 19:30.136
THE PLEIADES WERE THE DAUGHTERS
OF ATLAS THE TITAN

19:30.169 --> 19:31.971
AND SOME FLOOZY SEA NYMPH.

19:32.004 --> 19:32.972
WHAT ELSE?

19:33.005 --> 19:34.841
[ SIGHS ]

19:36.843 --> 19:38.345
"ANCIENT ASTRONOMERS
ONCE BELIEVED

19:38.378 --> 19:40.480
"THAT THE BRIGHTEST STAR
IN THE PLEIADES, ALCYONE,

19:40.513 --> 19:41.948
"WAS THE CENTER
OF THE UNIVERSE,

19:41.981 --> 19:43.650
AROUND WHICH ALL
THE HEAVENS REVOLVED."

19:43.683 --> 19:48.488
"CENTER OF THE UNIVERSE."

19:48.521 --> 19:50.189
DANIEL?

19:56.363 --> 19:59.299
AH...

19:59.332 --> 20:01.501
AL-CY-ON...

20:01.534 --> 20:04.671
UH, FREEMASONS.

20:04.704 --> 20:08.174
ILLUMINATI.

20:08.207 --> 20:09.742
"THE ORDER OF ALCYONE --

20:09.776 --> 20:12.111
ONE OF THE MOST ANCIENT
AND POWERFUL SECRET SOCIETIES."

20:12.144 --> 20:14.747
UH, "SOME BELIEVE
THE ORDER'S SENIOR COUNCIL

20:14.781 --> 20:16.683
"HAS MANIPULATED
WORLD EVENTS

20:16.716 --> 20:19.051
"THROUGH THE APPOINTMENT
OF ITS MEMBERS

20:19.085 --> 20:21.354
"TO POSITIONS OF POWER
AND INFLUENCE.

20:21.388 --> 20:24.557
"THEIR ULTIMATE GOAL IS TO
CREATE A SINGLE WORLD GOVERNMENT

20:24.591 --> 20:28.461
WITH THE ORDER ITSELF
AT THE CENTER OF THE UNIVERSE."

20:28.495 --> 20:30.463
YOU DON'T BELIEVE
A SECRET SOCIETY

20:30.497 --> 20:31.864
IS MURDERING CONGRESSMEN.

20:31.898 --> 20:33.700
MAYBE!

20:33.733 --> 20:36.068
MAYBE SOME -- SOME MODERN-DAY
CABAL OF BUSINESSMEN

20:36.102 --> 20:38.671
LIKE CRAWFORD HAS ADOPTED
THE PHILOSOPHY OF THIS GROUP

20:38.705 --> 20:41.508
AND THEY'RE TRYING TO INSTALL
THEIR OWN PEOPLE IN GOVERNMENT

20:41.541 --> 20:43.009
TO SERVE THEIR
COMPANIES' INTERESTS.

20:43.042 --> 20:46.546
NOW YOU'RE SEEING
THE BIG PICTURE, PROFESSOR.

20:47.947 --> 20:49.916
A CUBAN -- REALLY?

20:49.949 --> 20:52.719
I ENJOY THE IRONY.

20:52.752 --> 20:55.221
NOW, THIS --
UH, THIS CONSPIRACY

20:55.254 --> 20:57.590
WAS NEVER ABOUT
GETTING PAULSON OUT.

20:57.624 --> 21:00.159
IT WAS ABOUT GETTING
HIS SUCCESSOR IN.

21:00.192 --> 21:02.662
SCOTT RYLAND.

21:02.695 --> 21:03.996
SOME VERY POWERFUL MEN

21:04.030 --> 21:05.665
MUST HAVE WANTED RYLAND
IN THAT SENATE SEAT.

21:05.698 --> 21:07.867
BUT KILLING PAULSON DOESN'T MAKE
HIS PROTéGé SENATOR.

21:07.900 --> 21:10.870
THIS IS CHICAGO,
PROFESSOR.

21:10.903 --> 21:14.106
REMEMBER WHAT HAPPENED HERE
WHEN I RAN FOR THE WHITE HOUSE?

21:26.553 --> 21:27.887
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

21:27.920 --> 21:30.723
DANIEL?

21:30.757 --> 21:33.560
IT'S 1960 ALL OVER AGAIN.

21:33.593 --> 21:35.828
REMEMBER JFK's ELECTION?

21:35.862 --> 21:37.464
THAT WAS A LITTLE
BEFORE MY TIME.

21:37.497 --> 21:39.031
THERE WAS THIS MAFIA BOSS,
SAM GIANCANA.

21:39.065 --> 21:40.400
THE RUMOR WAS,
HE STUFFED THE BALLOT

21:40.433 --> 21:42.134
AND STOLE CHICAGO
FOR THE DEMOCRATS.

21:42.168 --> 21:44.070
BUT IT'S A LOT EASIER TO STEAL
AN ELECTION THESE DAYS.

21:44.103 --> 21:46.439
ALL YOU GOT TO DO
IS PUSH A BUTTON.

21:49.108 --> 21:52.745
"VERTERON ACQUIRES
DOVER ELECTION SOLUTIONS."

21:52.779 --> 21:54.046
SO?

21:54.080 --> 21:55.982
SO, IT TURNS OUT
CRAWFORD'S COMPANY

21:56.015 --> 21:57.650
DOESN'T JUST MAKE AVIONICS.

21:57.684 --> 21:59.151
EIGHT MONTHS AGO, THEY BOUGHT
INTO A NEW BUSINESS --

21:59.185 --> 22:01.488
ELECTRONIC VOTING MACHINES.

22:01.521 --> 22:04.424
THOSE [BLEEP] MURDERED PAULSON
AND RIGGED THE ELECTION.

22:04.457 --> 22:06.125
THEY STOLE THAT SENATE SEAT
FOR SCOTT RYLAND.

22:08.094 --> 22:09.662
DANIEL WAS RIGHT.

22:09.696 --> 22:11.998
THE ELECTION RESULTS DON'T MATCH
UP WITH THE EXIT POLLING.

22:12.031 --> 22:14.767
THE COUNTIES IN BLUE WERE
PREDICTED TO GO FOR RYLAND.

22:14.801 --> 22:17.704
THE COUNTIES IN RED WERE
EXPECTED TO GO TO HIS OPPONENT.

22:19.205 --> 22:20.640
LOOKS LIKE A LANDSLIDE.

22:20.673 --> 22:22.475
EXCEPT THAT IS NOT
WHAT ACTUALLY HAPPENED.

22:22.509 --> 22:24.844
THESE ARE THE COUNTIES
THAT RYLAND ACTUALLY WON.

22:24.877 --> 22:26.312
Daniel: YOU SEE?

22:26.345 --> 22:28.781
A SLIM ENOUGH MARGIN,
IT LOOKS LIKE A SQUEAKER.

22:28.815 --> 22:31.784
WOULDN'T BE THE FIRST TIME
THE EXIT POLLS WERE WRONG.

22:31.818 --> 22:34.286
AND EVEN IF THE RESULTS
WERE TAMPERED WITH,

22:34.320 --> 22:35.788
HOW DO WE PROVE THAT?

22:35.822 --> 22:38.491
WESLEY BELIEVED THAT A --
THAT A VERTERON ENGINEER,

22:38.525 --> 22:40.460
BRIAN [FINGERS SNAP]
WILLINGHAM

22:40.493 --> 22:42.128
GOT WIND OF CRAWFORD'S PLAN
AND TURNED UP DEAD --

22:42.161 --> 22:43.463
UH, "SUICIDE."

22:43.496 --> 22:46.399
MAYBE IF THIS WILLINGHAM
FIGURED IT OUT,

22:46.433 --> 22:48.100
SOMEBODY ELSE
AT VERTERON DID, TOO.

22:48.134 --> 22:50.102
WE NEED THE NAMES AND ADDRESSES
OF ALL THEIR EMPLOYEES,

22:50.136 --> 22:52.071
ESPECIALLY THE ONES
IN THE ELECTION DIVISION.

22:56.342 --> 23:00.379
I WAS WORKING LATE THE NIGHT
BEFORE THE VOTE.

23:00.413 --> 23:03.049
I NOTICED THAT SOMEONE
HAD UPLOADED

23:03.082 --> 23:06.486
SOME KIND OF SOFTWARE UPDATE
TO THE D.R.E. SERVERS.

23:06.519 --> 23:07.787
D.R.E.?

23:07.820 --> 23:10.322
DIRECT RECORDING
ELECTRONIC VOTING.

23:10.356 --> 23:12.492
I DECOMPILED THE CODE,

23:12.525 --> 23:16.162
AND I DISCOVERED A VIRUS
HIDDEN INSIDE.

23:17.530 --> 23:19.065
[ SIGHS ]

23:19.098 --> 23:21.333
IT WAS DESIGNED TO ALTER
THE VOTING TABULATION

23:21.367 --> 23:23.503
ON EVERY MACHINE
THAT RECEIVED THE UPGRADE.

23:23.536 --> 23:27.073
SO YOU TOLD BRIAN WILLINGHAM
WHAT YOU'D FOUND.

23:29.208 --> 23:32.512
BRIAN WAS THE ONLY ONE
THAT I TRUSTED AT THE COMPANY.

23:32.545 --> 23:34.847
[ SIGHS ]

23:34.881 --> 23:37.817
HE STARTED ASKING
QUESTIONS.

23:37.850 --> 23:40.953
BUT THE C.E.O. WOULDN'T EVEN
GIVE HIM THE TIME OF DAY.

23:40.987 --> 23:43.089
SO...

23:43.122 --> 23:44.757
[ SIGHS ]

23:44.791 --> 23:46.726
HE HACKED INTO
CRAWFORD'S E-MAIL.

23:49.395 --> 23:51.864
DID HE TELL YOU
WHAT HE FOUND?

23:51.898 --> 23:54.534
HE WAS PRETTY CERTAIN

23:54.567 --> 23:56.603
THAT CRAWFORD WAS BEHIND
THE WHOLE THING.

23:56.636 --> 24:00.272
AND THERE WAS
SOMETHING ELSE.

24:00.306 --> 24:01.541
HE SAID THAT HE READ
IN THE E-MAILS

24:01.574 --> 24:02.842
THAT THERE WAS GOING TO BE

24:02.875 --> 24:03.910
SOME KIND OF BIG MEETING
AT VERTERON --

24:03.943 --> 24:07.714
SOME KIND OF
SENIOR COUNCIL.

24:07.747 --> 24:10.717
A LOT OF IMPORTANT PEOPLE
WERE GOING TO BE THERE...

24:10.750 --> 24:13.385
[ SIGHS ]
...INCLUDING SENATOR RYLAND.

24:13.419 --> 24:16.723
DID HE TELL YOU WHEN THIS
MEETING WAS GONNA TAKE PLACE?

24:16.756 --> 24:18.357
[ SIGHS ]

24:18.390 --> 24:20.459
I DON'T KNOW -- SOMETIME
AFTER RYLAND WAS SWORN IN.

24:20.493 --> 24:22.394
[ SIGHS ]

24:22.428 --> 24:27.066
WOULD YOU BE WILLING TO TESTIFY
TO WHAT YOU'VE TOLD US?

24:27.099 --> 24:29.736
YES.

24:29.769 --> 24:31.370
IT'LL BE HER WORD
AGAINST HIS.

24:31.403 --> 24:33.339
IF WE'RE GONNA GET CRAWFORD,
WE NEED HARD EVIDENCE.

24:44.350 --> 24:46.352
I MADE A COPY OF THE VIRUS.

24:54.360 --> 24:56.696
GET THIS DOWN TO CART
AND GET IT ANALYZED.

24:59.465 --> 25:01.100
MRS. PAULSON DIED FROM
CONGESTIVE HEART FAILURE

25:01.133 --> 25:03.836
BROUGHT ON BY ACUTE
RADIATION POISONING.

25:03.870 --> 25:05.337
DO YOU KNOW WHAT KIND?

25:05.371 --> 25:06.806
POLONIUM-210.

25:06.839 --> 25:09.842
I FOUND MASSIVE TRACES
IN HER HAIR AND BONE MARROW.

25:09.876 --> 25:12.011
SHOULD WE BE WEARING
LEAD SUITS?

25:12.044 --> 25:13.613
POLONIUM'S ONLY DANGEROUS
IF INGESTED.

25:13.646 --> 25:18.117
SHE CONSUMED ABOUT 10 MICROGRAMS
PROBABLY A WEEK AGO.

25:18.150 --> 25:20.452
COULD THIS HAVE BEEN
AN ACCIDENT?

25:20.486 --> 25:22.088
POLONIUM JUST DOESN'T EXIST
IN THESE QUANTITIES IN NATURE.

25:26.058 --> 25:27.860
SHE WAS ASSASSINATED.

25:27.894 --> 25:30.129
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

25:30.162 --> 25:33.800
MORETTI.

25:33.833 --> 25:36.936
OKAY.

25:36.969 --> 25:38.170
THAT WAS THE CART UNIT.

25:38.204 --> 25:39.205
THE FLASH DRIVE
THAT JANICE GAVE US,

25:39.238 --> 25:40.306
THERE'S NOTHING ON IT.

25:40.339 --> 25:41.708
AFTER EVERYTHING
SHE TOLD US,

25:41.741 --> 25:43.643
WHY WOULD SHE GIVE US
A BLANK FLASH DRIVE?

25:43.676 --> 25:45.477
IT DOESN'T MAKE ANY --
WHERE IS SHE NOW?

25:45.511 --> 25:47.980
PROTECTIVE CUSTODY --
EMISSARY HOTEL.

25:48.014 --> 25:50.650
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

25:50.683 --> 25:52.084
HOW LONG HAS SHE
BEEN IN THERE?

25:52.118 --> 25:53.653
SHE SAID SHE WASN'T
FEELING WELL.

25:53.686 --> 25:54.854
SHE WANTED TO TAKE
A NAP.

25:54.887 --> 25:56.388
AN HOUR AGO, MAYBE.

25:56.422 --> 25:58.057
OPEN THE DOOR.

25:58.090 --> 26:01.728
[ LOCK BEEPS ]

26:01.761 --> 26:03.763
JANICE!

26:07.066 --> 26:09.068
WE'RE TOO LATE.

26:11.370 --> 26:13.706
[ CLASSICAL MUSIC PLAYS ]

26:16.208 --> 26:17.677
[ MUSIC STOPS ]

26:17.710 --> 26:19.178
SO?

26:19.211 --> 26:20.346
SO,
I'VE BEEN REASSIGNED.

26:20.379 --> 26:21.547
WHY?!

26:21.580 --> 26:23.750
MEDICAL EXAMINER SAYS
THAT JANICE

26:23.783 --> 26:25.251
ALSO DIED FROM EXPOSURE
TO POLONIUM.

26:25.284 --> 26:27.119
THAT'S BECAUSE CRAWFORD
OR SOMEBODY AT VERTERON

26:27.153 --> 26:28.988
REALIZED SHE WAS A LOOSE END
AND POISONED HER.

26:29.021 --> 26:31.123
WASHINGTON
ISN'T BUYING THAT.

26:31.157 --> 26:33.025
THEY'RE CONSIDERING THIS
A PUBLIC HEALTH CRISIS.

26:33.059 --> 26:34.393
THE PRIORITY RIGHT NOW

26:34.426 --> 26:36.262
IS FINDING THE SOURCE
OF THE POLONIUM

26:36.295 --> 26:37.764
SO THAT NO ONE ELSE
GETS SICK.

26:37.797 --> 26:39.866
THESE WOMEN DIDN'T DIE
BECAUSE A RADIOISOTOPE

26:39.899 --> 26:41.367
SEEPED INTO
THEIR TAP WATER.

26:41.400 --> 26:42.835
IT'S LIKE WESLEY SAID --

26:42.869 --> 26:44.704
ANYBODY THAT GETS CLOSE
TO THE TRUTH GETS KILLED.

26:44.737 --> 26:46.438
DANIEL,
THERE'S NOTHING I CAN DO.

26:46.472 --> 26:48.374
WE CAN'T BACK OFF NOW,
KATE.

26:48.407 --> 26:51.110
THINK ABOUT WHAT JANICE SAID
ABOUT THE -- THE BIG MEETING.

26:51.143 --> 26:53.846
THAT COULD BE THE KEY TO
BREAKING THIS WHOLE CONSPIRACY.

26:53.880 --> 26:56.783
WE HAVE NO IDEA WHEN THAT
MEETING IS SUPPOSED TO HAPPEN.

26:56.816 --> 26:58.284
FOR ALL WE KNOW,
IT ALREADY DID.

26:58.317 --> 27:02.121
JFK: SHE'S ENTIRELY MISTAKEN,
PROFESSOR.

27:02.154 --> 27:03.790
OF COURSE YOU KNOW
WHEN IT'S HAPPENING.

27:03.823 --> 27:06.325
WHAT?

27:07.593 --> 27:09.128
THE ANSWER
YOU'RE LOOKING FOR...

27:09.161 --> 27:12.398
IS IN THE STARS.

27:12.431 --> 27:16.068
THE MEETING IS TOMORROW MORNING,
JUST BEFORE SUNRISE.

27:16.102 --> 27:18.070
YOU'RE GETTING ALL THIS
FROM AN ASTRONOMY BOOK?

27:18.104 --> 27:19.405
THE PLEIADES.

27:19.438 --> 27:21.173
REMEMBER, WE SAW THEM
IN CRAWFORD'S OFFICE,

27:21.207 --> 27:22.909
AND ALCOTT WROTE IT
IN HIS NOTEBOOK.

27:22.942 --> 27:24.576
WHAT DOES THIS HAVE TO DO

27:24.610 --> 27:25.978
WITH WHAT TIME THE MEETING
IS SUPPOSED TO TAKE PLACE?

27:26.012 --> 27:27.246
THE HELIACAL RISING.

27:27.279 --> 27:28.815
LISTEN. LISTEN.

27:28.848 --> 27:31.183
"THE PLEIADES ARE A GROUP
OF STARS THAT RISE EVERY DAY,

27:31.217 --> 27:32.484
"JUST LIKE THE SUN,

27:32.518 --> 27:34.253
"BUT ONE DAY A YEAR,
THEY RISE BEFORE DAWN

27:34.286 --> 27:36.588
"AND ARE VISIBLE
ABOVE THE EASTERN HORIZON.

27:36.622 --> 27:39.091
THIS FIRST APPEARANCE IS KNOWN
AS THE HELIACAL RISING,"

27:39.125 --> 27:41.260
WHICH, THIS YEAR,
TAKES PLACE...

27:41.293 --> 27:42.594
TOMORROW MORNING.

27:42.628 --> 27:44.596
WE'VE GOT TO GET TO VERTERON
BEFORE DAWN.

27:44.630 --> 27:45.932
IT'S THE ONLY WAY
WE'RE GONNA FIGURE OUT

27:45.965 --> 27:47.399
WHO ALL
THE CONSPIRATORS ARE.

27:47.433 --> 27:49.168
DANIEL, I FEEL LIKE
THAT'S A LOT OF FAITH

27:49.201 --> 27:50.770
TO PUT IN A SCRIBBLE
IN A NOTEBOOK.

27:50.803 --> 27:53.139
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

27:57.977 --> 27:59.779
DANIEL PIERCE,

27:59.812 --> 28:02.749
YOU ARE UNDER ARREST FOR
THE MURDER OF WESLEY SUMTER.

28:15.828 --> 28:18.297
THIS VIDEO'S A FAKE.

28:18.330 --> 28:21.934
NO, IT WAS JUST ENHANCED
BY THE CART UNIT.

28:21.968 --> 28:23.102
I AM BEING SET UP!

28:23.135 --> 28:26.172
OKAY.
WHO'S SETTING YOU UP?

28:26.205 --> 28:27.673
I HAVEN'T
THE FAINTEST IDEA,

28:27.706 --> 28:28.474
BUT IF YOU WANT TO SEARCH
MY HOUSE F-FOR A CROSSBOW,

28:28.507 --> 28:30.109
BE MY GUEST.

28:30.142 --> 28:32.344
DID YOU HAVE ANYTHING TO DO
WITH THE OTHER DEATHS?

28:32.378 --> 28:34.680
AREDAVID ALCOTT...S ]

28:34.713 --> 28:35.848
BRIAN WILLINGHAM...

28:35.882 --> 28:37.683
HELEN PAULSON.

28:37.716 --> 28:41.187
SURE, SURE. YES, I-I-I-I HAVE
A SECRET STASH OF POLONIUM-210

28:41.220 --> 28:42.755
IN MY MEDICINE CABINET.

28:44.223 --> 28:46.192
KATE...
KATE, Y-YOU BELIEVE ME.

28:46.225 --> 28:48.194
I-I-I DIDN'T --
I DIDN'T KILL WESLEY SUMTER

28:48.227 --> 28:50.462
OR ANYBODY ELSE,
FOR THAT MATTER.

28:50.496 --> 28:54.533
DANIEL, I KNOW THAT YOU ARE NOT
CAPABLE OF HURTING ANYONE.

28:55.768 --> 28:59.939
IF YOU WERE IN
THE RIGHT FRAME OF MIND.

29:02.241 --> 29:04.043
BUT IT IS POSSIBLE

29:04.076 --> 29:05.878
THAT YOU DIDN'T KNOW
WHAT YOU WERE DOING

29:05.912 --> 29:08.447
WHEN YOU PULLED
THAT TRIGGER.

29:10.116 --> 29:11.650
OH, KATE...

29:11.683 --> 29:15.354
JFK: THERE'S A FOX
IN THE HENHOUSE, PROFESSOR.

29:15.387 --> 29:18.524
THIS G-MAN WAS ONE
OF THE CONSPIRATORS.

29:18.557 --> 29:22.228
PROBERT?

29:22.261 --> 29:23.930
YEAH?

29:23.963 --> 29:27.166
HE HAD CUSTODY OF THE DRIVE
THAT WAS MYSTERIOUSLY ERASED.

29:27.199 --> 29:29.301
HE WAS FIRST ON THE SCENE

29:29.335 --> 29:31.337
AFTER THE SNIPER KILLED
YOUR FRIEND.

29:33.239 --> 29:36.208
YOU...
YOU MOVED WESLEY'S BODY.

29:36.242 --> 29:38.310
DANIEL,
THIS ISN'T HELPING.

29:38.344 --> 29:40.880
WHO ARE YOU WORKING FOR --
CRAWFORD, SENATOR RYLAND?

29:40.913 --> 29:42.882
LOOK, PIERCE,
I KNOW THAT YOU THINK

29:42.915 --> 29:44.716
I'VE ALWAYS HAD IT OUT
FOR YOU.

29:44.750 --> 29:46.552
THE TRUTH IS,
I CARE ABOUT YOU.

29:46.585 --> 29:49.421
BUT YOU ARE
A VERY SICK MAN.

29:49.455 --> 29:52.258
NOW, WE'RE GONNA DO EVERYTHING
THAT WE CAN TO MAKE SURE

29:52.291 --> 29:54.426
YOU GET THE VERY BEST LAWYER

29:54.460 --> 29:56.628
SO THAT YOU CAN GET THE HELP
THAT YOU NEED.

29:59.866 --> 30:00.867
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

30:05.637 --> 30:08.140
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

30:13.379 --> 30:17.783
WHEN WE GET BACK, THE S.A.I.C.
[ ELECTRICITY CRACKLES ]

30:17.816 --> 30:20.086
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

30:20.119 --> 30:21.753
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

30:21.787 --> 30:25.724
THROWING AWAY ANY CHANCE
OF FUTURE PROMOTION.

30:25.757 --> 30:27.927
DANIEL, YOU MIGHT BE CRAZY,
BUT YOU ARE NO KILLER.

30:27.960 --> 30:29.161
THAT TAPE WAS DOCTORED.

30:29.195 --> 30:30.462
I THOUGHT
YOU DIDN'T BELIEVE ME.

30:30.496 --> 30:32.098
PROBERT WAS STANDING
RIGHT THERE.

30:32.131 --> 30:33.732
I HAD TO PRETEND
TO AGREE WITH HIM.

30:33.765 --> 30:35.334
HIT THE PARKING GARAGE,
WOULD YOU?

30:39.005 --> 30:40.606
[ GRUNTS ]

30:40.639 --> 30:43.475
GREAT.
NOW WHAT DO WE DO WITH HIM?

30:43.509 --> 30:45.978
LET ME WORRY ABOUT THAT, OKAY?
NOW, YOU NEED TO LEAVE.

30:46.012 --> 30:47.980
THAT DOOR WILL LET YOU OUT
INTO THE ALLEY.

30:48.014 --> 30:49.882
YOU CAN'T.
I'M GOING TO VERTERON.

30:49.916 --> 30:52.151
YOU'RE NOT GOING INTO
THAT BUILDING BY YOURSELF!

30:52.184 --> 30:53.986
LISTEN, I'M JUST GONNA GO
INTO THE CONFERENCE ROOM
AND TRY TO PLANT A WIRE.

30:54.020 --> 30:55.321
I'LL ONLY BE IN THERE
A FEW MINUTES.

30:55.354 --> 30:56.989
DON'T YOU NEED A COURT ORDER
FOR THAT?

30:57.023 --> 30:59.091
I JUST TASED MY PARTNER
AND DUMPED HIM IN A TRUNK!

30:59.125 --> 31:01.093
I'M NOT EXACTLY DOING THINGS
BY THE BOOK TODAY!

31:01.127 --> 31:03.629
LISTEN, JUST LAY LOW
FOR A FEW HOURS.

31:03.662 --> 31:06.765
I WILL MEET YOU
IN MILLENNIUM PARK AT SUNRISE.

31:06.798 --> 31:08.800
BUT, DANIEL, I...WAIT!

31:28.887 --> 31:30.556
[ SIGHS ]

31:35.461 --> 31:37.329
[ SIREN WAILS ]

31:41.833 --> 31:43.635
SHE TOLD ME TO MEET HER
AT SUNRISE.

31:43.669 --> 31:44.937
SHE SHOULD BE HERE
BY NOW.

31:44.971 --> 31:46.638
RELAX, PROFESSOR.
SHE'S A PROFESSIONAL.

31:46.672 --> 31:49.641
SHE'S GOT A LOT MORE ON THE BALL
THAN ANY OF HOOVER'S BOYS.

31:49.675 --> 31:51.810
SHE'LL BE HERE.

31:51.843 --> 31:54.313
[ SIGHS ] NO, NO, NO,
S-SOMETHING'S HAPPENED.

31:54.346 --> 31:56.448
SHE'S IN TROUBLE.

31:56.482 --> 31:59.718
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]
I'M GOING AFTER HER.

32:14.933 --> 32:18.337
I DON'T SUPPOSE
YOU KNOW THE CODE.

32:18.370 --> 32:20.372
ACTUALLY...

32:22.274 --> 32:24.243
...I'M PRETTY SURE I DO.

32:24.276 --> 32:26.278
[ BEEPING ]

32:28.280 --> 32:30.416
PLEIADES.
OF COURSE.

32:30.449 --> 32:32.618
[ LOCK DISENGAGES ]

32:35.954 --> 32:38.924
Ryland: THANKS TO
YOUR UNWAVERING SUPPORT,

32:38.957 --> 32:42.094
I NOW STAND BEFORE YOU
AS A UNITED STATES SENATOR.

32:42.128 --> 32:44.596
THIS VICTORY BELONGS
TO EVERYONE HERE

32:44.630 --> 32:46.598
AT THIS HISTORIC CONFERENCE.

32:46.632 --> 32:49.101
AND IT BRINGS US
ONE STEP CLOSER

32:49.135 --> 32:52.104
TO ACHIEVING
OUR ULTIMATE OBJECTIVE --

32:52.138 --> 32:55.774
DOMINION OVER
THE AFFAIRS OF...

32:55.807 --> 32:57.609
OH.

32:57.643 --> 33:00.246
THIS IS AN UNEXPECTED
SURPRISE.

33:07.986 --> 33:12.124
MR. PRESIDENT, IT'S A PLEASURE
TO FINALLY MEET YOU.

33:12.158 --> 33:13.225
[ APPLAUSE ]

33:13.259 --> 33:14.793
PLEASURE'S MINE,
SENATOR.

33:14.826 --> 33:16.195
WHAT THE [BLEEP]
GOING ON HERE?

33:23.502 --> 33:25.971
SIR, YOU'LL HAVE TO
COME WITH ME.

33:26.004 --> 33:27.806
GET YOUR HANDS OFF ME.

33:27.839 --> 33:29.508
LET GO OF ME!
LET GO OF ME!

33:29.541 --> 33:32.611
I KNOW WHAT'S GOING ON HERE!
YOU'RE NOT FOOLING ANYONE!

33:32.644 --> 33:34.480
YOU'RE A MURDERER, CRAWFORD!
YOU'RE A KILLER!

33:34.513 --> 33:36.282
YOU'RE ALL KILLERS!
THE WORLD IS GONNA KNOW!

33:36.315 --> 33:38.117
IT'S ME.
LISTEN, IT'S ME!

33:38.150 --> 33:40.486
YOU'RE A MURDERER, CRAWFORD!
DOC, IT'S MAX.

33:40.519 --> 33:41.987
I KNOW WHAT'S GOING ON
IN THIS ROOM!

33:42.020 --> 33:43.822
THE WORLD WILL KNOW!

33:43.855 --> 33:45.357
DOC, LISTEN, PLEASE!

33:45.391 --> 33:47.326
LISTEN TO ME, DOC!
IT'S MAX!ALCYONE!

33:47.359 --> 33:48.560
LOOK AT ME!

33:48.594 --> 33:50.796
LOOK AT ME.
IT'S MAX --

33:50.829 --> 33:52.831
MAX LEWICKI, DOC.

33:54.966 --> 33:57.569
MAX?
HOW DID YOU --

33:57.603 --> 34:00.472
I'M HERE, DOC.
OKAY? YOU'RE ALL RIGHT.

34:00.506 --> 34:02.007
YOU'RE GONNA BE
J[ GASPS ]

34:02.040 --> 34:05.977
I'VE GOT YOU.
I'VE GOT YOU, DOC, OKAY?

34:06.011 --> 34:08.680
I'VE GOT YOU.

34:19.425 --> 34:20.726
HOW DID I GET HERE?

34:20.759 --> 34:23.495
WHAT DO YOU MEAN, DOC?
YOU'RE HOME.

34:23.529 --> 34:25.030
NO, NO, NO.

34:25.063 --> 34:28.167
I WAS DOWNTOWN JUST --
JUST A FEW MINUTES AGO!

34:28.200 --> 34:30.669
DOC, I...I THINK
YOU'RE CONFUSED.

34:30.702 --> 34:32.338
NO, NO, I'M NOT,
I'M NOT.

34:32.371 --> 34:34.173
WHAT THE [BLEEP]
HAPPENED?

34:34.206 --> 34:36.508
NO.
[ MUMBLES ]

34:36.542 --> 34:39.345
I DON'T KNOW.
DOC, I JUST GOT HOME.

34:39.378 --> 34:40.612
DANIEL?

34:40.646 --> 34:43.482
KATE!

34:43.515 --> 34:45.016
OH, KATE!

34:48.154 --> 34:49.688
THANK GOD
YOU'RE ALL RIGHT.

34:49.721 --> 34:51.357
I WAS SO WORRIED
ABOUT YOU.

34:51.390 --> 34:53.192
WHY?

34:53.225 --> 34:55.194
WHY DID YOU NOT MEET ME
AT MILLENNIUM PARK?

34:55.227 --> 34:57.196
MILLENNIUM PARK?

34:57.229 --> 34:58.530
I WENT IN THE BUILDING
TO FIND YOU.

34:58.564 --> 34:59.865
I KNOW YOU SAID NOT TO,

34:59.898 --> 35:01.433
BUT THEN --
T-THEY MUST HAVE DRUGGED ME.

35:01.467 --> 35:03.034
THEY MUST HAVE DRUGGED ME
BECAUSE THE NEXT THING I KNEW,

35:03.068 --> 35:06.872
I-I-I WAS HERE.
I-I WAS HOME.

35:06.905 --> 35:08.707
DANIEL,
THE LAST TIME I SAW YOU

35:08.740 --> 35:11.143
WAS WHEN I DROVE YOU HOME
FROM THE UNIVERSITY

35:11.177 --> 35:13.111
AFTER WE LOOKED
FOR WESLEY'S BODY.

35:15.981 --> 35:20.051
THAT WAS TWO DAYS AGO.
YOU REMEMBER THAT?

35:20.085 --> 35:21.920
YES, I REMEMBER THAT!
AND THEN YOU --

35:21.953 --> 35:23.722
THEN YOU CAME BACK
THAT AFTERNOON,

35:23.755 --> 35:25.891
AND YOU G-- YOU HAD THAT --
T-T-THE -- THIS.

35:25.924 --> 35:27.058
HERE, HERE.

35:27.092 --> 35:28.160
PLAY IT. PLAY IT.

35:28.194 --> 35:30.529
JUST PLAY IT!

35:30.562 --> 35:31.797
IT'S A RECORDING

35:31.830 --> 35:34.233
O-O-OF THE SNIPER
O-ON THAT DISK.

35:34.266 --> 35:36.902
A STUDENT -- A STUDENT
CAUGHT IT ON HIS CELLPHONE.

35:36.935 --> 35:38.103
AND THEN PROBERT --

35:38.136 --> 35:39.871
PROBERT, WITH
HIS COMPUTER TRICKERY --

35:39.905 --> 35:42.741
PUT MY HEAD ON THE
SNIPER'S BODY -- TELL HIM!

35:42.774 --> 35:45.277
SURE, DANIEL,
LET'S TAKE A LOOK.

35:47.279 --> 35:49.147
[ SNIFFS ]

35:51.783 --> 35:52.984
WHAT THE [BLEEP] IS THIS?

35:53.018 --> 35:55.086
IT'S AN fMRI SCAN.

35:55.120 --> 35:57.155
YOU WANTED ME
TO BURN IT TO A DVD

35:57.189 --> 35:59.157
SO YOU COULD SHOW IT
IN CLASS.

36:00.959 --> 36:02.761
[ GASPS ]

36:02.794 --> 36:05.264
COME ON, DOC.

36:05.297 --> 36:06.598
I...

36:06.632 --> 36:09.435
COME ON, DOC,
LET'S GET YOU WASHED UP.

36:09.468 --> 36:11.503
KATE...

36:11.537 --> 36:13.372
JUST GO WITH MAX.
I'LL BE RIGHT HERE.

36:21.813 --> 36:24.316
IIT'S OKAY.

36:36.161 --> 36:37.829
I-I-I'M NOT AN INVALID,
LEWICKI.

36:37.863 --> 36:39.465
I'M CAPABLE
OF WASHING MYSELF.

36:39.498 --> 36:40.799
DOC, I'D RA--

36:40.832 --> 36:42.167
GIVE ME A LITTLE
TIME ALONE, PLEASE.

36:42.200 --> 36:43.669
I'D RATHER STAY
IF THAT'S ALL RIGHT.

36:43.702 --> 36:45.371
JUST I-I-I'M NOT GONNA
HURT MYSELF, OKAY?

36:45.404 --> 36:46.872
IF THAT'S WHAT
YOU'RE WORRIED ABOUT.

36:46.905 --> 36:48.307
PLEASE,
JUST GET THE [BLEEP] OUT.

36:48.340 --> 36:49.675
[ DOOR SLAMS ]

37:05.691 --> 37:08.159
SOME OF THESE
ARE ARTICLES

37:08.193 --> 37:11.330
DANIEL SAID
HIS FRIEND WESLEY GAVE HIM.

37:11.363 --> 37:15.000
DOC'S BEEN BUSY.

37:15.033 --> 37:16.668
DOESN'T LOOK LIKE
HE'S LEFT THE HOUSE

37:16.702 --> 37:19.305
SINCE YOU DROPPED HIM OFF.

37:28.680 --> 37:31.483
[ WATER RUNNING ]

37:31.517 --> 37:33.184
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

37:36.254 --> 37:37.255
[ GRUNTS ]

37:41.893 --> 37:44.029
DANIEL, YOU NEED HELP.

37:44.062 --> 37:46.865
THIS IS A MAJOR
ESCALATION.

37:46.898 --> 37:49.701
IT'S ONE THING TO HAVE VISIONS
OF JOHN KENNEDY,

37:49.735 --> 37:53.539
BUT YOU'VE SPENT THE ENTIRE
WEEKEND IN A DELUSIONAL STATE.

37:53.572 --> 37:56.174
[ SIGHS ]
I MUST HAVE KNOWN [SNIFFS]

37:56.207 --> 37:58.510
ON SOME LEVEL
THAT IT WASN'T REAL.

37:58.544 --> 38:01.012
T-THAT'S -- THAT'S WHY I MADE
MYSELF SNAP OUT OF IT.

38:01.046 --> 38:02.213
BULL[BLEEP]

38:02.247 --> 38:04.716
YOU'D STILL BE WANDERING
THE HOUSE,

38:04.750 --> 38:08.420
TALKING TO THE WALLS IF MAX
HADN'T COME HOME WHEN HE DID.

38:08.454 --> 38:11.457
WHAT IF HE'D LEFT
FOR A WEEK?

38:13.291 --> 38:16.462
WHAT WOULD HAVE HAPPENED
TO YOU THEN?

38:29.641 --> 38:31.943
I SHOULD HAVE STARTED
TAKING THESE WEEKS AGO

38:31.977 --> 38:34.946
WHEN I HAD THE PRESCRIPTION
FILLED, BUT...

38:34.980 --> 38:38.617
I CONVINCED MYSELF
I DIDN'T NEED THEM.

38:43.188 --> 38:46.492
IT'S TOO LATE TO START THIS
ON YOUR OWN.

38:46.525 --> 38:49.094
YOU NEED TO GO
TO THE HOSPITAL.

38:49.127 --> 38:50.596
I DO THAT, THEY'RE GONNA
PUT ME ON SOMETHING

38:50.629 --> 38:51.763
A LOT STRONGER
THAN THESE.

38:51.797 --> 38:54.433
MAYBE THAT'S WHAT
YOU NEED.

38:54.466 --> 38:57.436
WHAT I NEED...

38:57.469 --> 38:59.605
IS TO BE WITH YOU.

39:02.641 --> 39:07.946
TRYING TO KEEP ME AROUND IS
WHAT GOT YOU INTO THIS MESS.

39:07.979 --> 39:10.281
FOR THE SAKE
OF YOUR SANITY

39:10.315 --> 39:12.951
AND EVERYTHING ELSE
THAT YOU CARE ABOUT,

39:12.984 --> 39:15.421
YOU NEED TO LET ME GO.

39:23.829 --> 39:27.298
IT'LL BE ALL RIGHT.

39:27.332 --> 39:29.167
[ BREATHES SHAKILY ]

39:34.440 --> 39:35.641
[ CRYING ]

39:40.746 --> 39:42.714
THAT WESLEY GUY --

39:42.748 --> 39:44.883
DOC GOT A LETTER
FROM HIM RIGHT BEFORE I LEFT,

39:44.916 --> 39:47.419
AND...NOW HE'S DEAD?

39:47.453 --> 39:50.021
FRANKLY, MAX,
I'M NOT EVEN SURE

39:50.055 --> 39:52.558
